Mobile Home Parks Must Be Between 4 And 15 Acres In Size With A 50ft Perimeter Buffer. They Must Set Aside 15% Of The Park For Common Recreation. Each Lot In A Mobile Home Park Must Have A Road Setback Of 20ft, Lot Line Setback Of 15ft, Road Frontage Of 50ft, And A Minimum Depth Of 100ft. Each Lot Must Have 2 Parking Spots And Must Receive A Nonporous Pad At Least Four Inches Thick.
